## Environment files (contain sensitive API keys)
# Ignore any .env variants anywhere
**/.env
**/.env.*
# But keep templates checked in
!**/.env.template
!**/config.py.template

## Configuration
# Do NOT ignore tracked config files; rely on env vars instead.
# If you have a local override, use config.local.py and keep it ignored:
config.local.py
backend/config.local.py

